         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne ¶ 1/7/77. ¶ To the Cavalier Marinucci, ¶ Consul General for Italy ¶ Melbourne...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">77.07.01</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Luigi Marinucci</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">Reale Istituto Veneto de scienze, lettere ed arti, Venice.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">MS annotation: 'Communicato all'Istituto il ringraziamento nell'adunanza 29 Luglio 1877' [Communicated to the Institute at the meeting on 29 July 1877]. See also M to A. De Zigno, 6 June 1877.</p>
               </note>Melbourne</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">1/7/77.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">To the Cavalier Marinucci,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Consul General for Italy</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I felt highly gratified, to receive from his Excellency the Minister of Foreign affairs of Italy through you the intimation, that the distinguished Royal Venetian Institute of sciences, letters and arts has done me the honor, to enrol me a Corresponding member, and I have to acknowledge the receipt of the beautiful diploma<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Reale Istituto Veneto de Scienze, Lettere ed Arti to M, 25 March 1877.</p>
               </note> which accompanied his Excellency's communication.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>May I ask you, to express to his Excellency my grateful appreciation of the distinction, so generously and unexpectedly conferred on me by a scientific union of such great celebrity; and let me offer my assurance, that I will endeavour to merit the confidence of the Venetian savants in my ability and readiness to cooperate in their scientific labors. I reflect on this new mark of honor from your country with particular pleasure, as from your great Kingdom I have been so frequently encouraged in my literary work.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">I am, honored Chevalier,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>your regardful</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller, M.D., Ph.D.</p>
         </div>
      </body>
